sentence: Hundreds  of  people  have  been  killed  on  both  sides,  and  an  unknown  number  of  Israelis  have  been  taken  hostage.
In  the  first  day  of  attacks  and  fighting,  at  least  250  Israelis  were  killed,  and  more  than  1,000  wounded.
More  than  230  Palestinians  were  killed,  with  nearly  2,000  injured,  according  to  health  officials  in  Gaza.

The  head  of  a  southern  Israeli  regional  council  was  fatally  shot  by  Palestinian  militants  in  Kfar  Aza,  a  council  spokeswoman  told  Israel's  public  broadcaster,  and  one  woman  was  reportedly  killed  by  rocket  fire  in  southern  Israel.

The  head  of  a  southern  Israeli  regional  council  was  fatally  shot  by  Palestinian  militants  in  Kfar  Aza,  a  council  spokeswoman  told  Israel's  public  broadcaster,  and  one  woman  was  reportedly  killed  by  rocket  fire  in  southern  Israel.
